## 📊 Featured Projects

### 🔹 HR Analytics Dashboard (Power BI)
Executive-level HR dashboard providing workforce performance insights including employee demographics, promotion readiness, attrition indicators, and service tenure distribution using advanced DAX measures and interactive KPI visualizations.

### 🔹 ABC Business License Analysis (Tableau)
Comprehensive business license data analysis project including data modeling, transformation, KPI design, and interactive dashboards to support decision-making and trend analysis.

### 🔹 Air Quality ML Prediction App (Streamlit)
End-to-end Machine Learning project including EDA, feature engineering, model training, evaluation, and deployment using Streamlit for interactive prediction.

